Deferral of the Subcommittee Meeting 

The meeting of the Subcommittee on Landmarks, Public Siting and Maritime Uses scheduled for Monday, May 17, 2010 at 11:00 a.m. has been deferred to the next scheduled meeting date of Tuesday, June 1, 2010 at the regularly scheduled time.
